{"tid":1244070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家政府同市民關係可以用呢兩句黎概括","createTime":"2019-06-19T17:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:35:50.000Z","uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c1bfd67a27e1cad68332555a6e12874ebf21e7","tid":1244070,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"其實你不愛我 才共我拉鋸拔河<br />\n凡事也不放過 盡全力摧毀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都有人提過 <br />\n大家記住 今次呢一役只係防止香港繼續惡化<br />\n<br />\n點解會造成今時今日咁既局面？<br />\n係因為政府唔係以民為本 為市民推政策 做實事<br />\n反而掛住刷大陸鞋 甘心做扯線公仔<br />\n一切都係源自香港仲未有民選政府 回顧幾年前爭取真普選正正就係爭取緊呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都知大家已經好攰 資訊過多、對政府既失望等等都令人好氣餒<br />\n之後仲有惡法、反智方案推緊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打完呢一役先係香港人真正反擊、推動香港進步既時候！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爭取真普選！爭取返一個以民為本既政府先係一勞永逸既做法</span><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係香港人之後實有排煩 最後只會消磨晒自己意志冇心冇力再出聲<br />\n慢慢令香港成為一個平平無奇既大陸城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff9a9292391d353f6d299d80de83f2c6423c76c","tid":1244070,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:05:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf3f15f607cfd7a4da79126e2a39843b05477fb","tid":1244070,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"put<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23b1ff1b99d443d16ee797146c2781c8359080e","tid":1244070,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b709a54027d3edc3c4cf7372b23cc82af4bac030","tid":1244070,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:06:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"530dca163d